                  <ul>
                    <li>They have an extra environment tag: sea, land, air, void, earth, or something stranger.</li>
                    <li>You have advantage on physical actions when piloting it.</li>
                    <li>They're giant and can fight Behemoths on equal terms.</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p><span class="sheet-move-trigger">Every time the you use it</span> pick one:</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Erase Surplus: Transport or Surplus: Energy.</li>
                    <li>It pollutes: gain Need: Medicine or Need: Land.</li>
                    <li>It could break down or blow up at any moment.</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
    
