                  <p>When your Family gains something that furthers their tenet, hold 1. When an emissary of your Family – including your Character – draws on this vision of future perfection, spend 1 hold to:</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Get an insight towards your current goal.</li>
                    <li>Ignore all penalties and Disadvantage for a single roll.</li>
                    <li>Plant the seeds of your faith in the mind of another.</li>
                  </ul>
