                </div>
                <div class="sheet-family-move-body">
                  <p>You didn't turn your body into your canvas because you wanted to be different, but because you wanted to become and express who you truly are: a monster, inhuman, otherworldly. Your characters can always substitute Sway for Force moves, but have Disadvantage on attempts to use <strong>Familiar Face</strong> or <strong>Find Common Ground</strong> on anyone who isn't an artist, rebel or outcast.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
