                </div>
              </div>
    
              <div class="sheet-family-move">
                <div class="sheet-family-move-title-wrapper">
                  <input type="checkbox" class="sheet-Moves-Syndicate" name="attr_Moves-Syndicate5">
                  <h3>People of the Sun</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="sheet-family-move-body">
                  <p>You have infiltrated every human Family or Faction. <em>When you roll</em> <strong>Subterfuge</strong> <em>against them,</em> you can spend Treaty on them 1-for-1 to choose extra items from the list. Also, you have a finger on the Homeland people's pulse. <em>When any other faction triggers</em> <storng>In Want</storng>, you can be the one who chooses what crisis they suffer if you wish.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
