        <div class="sheet-Cultivators">
          <div class="sheet-treaty-history-wrapper">
            <div class="sheet-treaty">
              <h2>Treaty</h2>
              <p><span class="sheet-move-trigger">When you freely give someone the perfect resource to solve a problem,</span> gain 1-Treaty on them.</p>
              <div class="sheet-treaty-wrapper">
                <div class="sheet-treaty-head">
