                        Platform</b> After analysing the current scene, roll +Lore. On a 10+, ask 2 questions. On a 7-9,
                      ask 1.
                      <ul>
                        <li>What, if anything, is hidden here?</li>
                        <li>What, if anything, is hazardous here?</li>
                        <li>What, if anything, is valuable here?</li>
                        <li>What, if anything, is vulnerable here?</li>
                      </ul>
