                      <p><input type="checkbox" class="sheet-Moves-Machine" name="attr_Moves-Machine5"> <b>Tactical
                          Computer</b> Your tactical analysis and comms all but guarantee your team’s safety. You can
                        always respond to a <b>Call for Aid</b> with Lore, even remotely. When you have time to assess
                        an enemy before acting, you can <b>Fiercely Assault</b> with +Lore.
