              sheltered and fed.</p>
            <p><input type="checkbox" class="sheet-Role-Reaver" name="attr_Role-Reaver-Agent"> <b>Agent:</b> Mark when
              you raid under your Family’s orders. Name the treasure you're hunting, the GM says why it's particularly
              important to its owner.</p>
            <p><input type="checkbox" class="sheet-Role-Reaver" name="attr_Role-Reaver-Rebel"> <b>Rebel:</b> Mark when
              you raid your own Family. Name a faction that now considers you a hero.</p>
            <p><input type="checkbox" class="sheet-Role-Reaver" name="attr_Role-Reaver-Outsider"> <b>Outsider:</b> Mark
              when you abandon everything and disappear into your chosen Hostile Grounds. Return at any moment when you
              think you're needed; the GM says what came back with you.</p>
            <p><i>When you mark a role in play, raise a stat by 1 or get a new move. If you mark all roles retire your
                character as soon as is convenient, using as many aspects of your Death Move as you wish.</i></p>
