            <b>Moves</b>
            <i>You get this move:</i>
            <p><input type="checkbox" class="sheet-Moves-Reaver" name="attr_Moves-Reaver1" checked="true"> <b>My
                Kingdom, My Rules</b> <i> Thanks to your heritage, strange tech or pure grit, you’re most comfortable in
                some region outside the safety of the Homeland: the precarious ruins, the deep seas, the immaterial
                digital realms, off-world void, tunnels underground, or something else. </p>
            <p>You are perfectly adapted to that harsh reality and have Advantage there. Also pick 2 to describe the
              method of transport you use to travel to the Homeland and back: </p>
            <p><input type="checkbox" class="sheet-Vehicle-Reaver" name="attr_Vehicle-Reaver1">It makes the trip
              quickly.</p>
