              already changing them.</p>
            <p><input type="checkbox" class="sheet-Role-Remnant" name="attr_Role-Remnant-Agent"> <b>Agent:</b> Mark and
              hold 1 when you advise a project with the wisdom of a fallen age. Spend the hold to reveal a forgotten
              principle or theory the project secretly benefits from.</p>
            <p><input type="checkbox" class="sheet-Role-Remnant" name="attr_Role-Remnant-Rebel"> <b>Rebel:</b> Mark when
