              when a group’s relying on you to find a crucial component. Say who else is looking for it.</p>
            <p><input type="checkbox" class="sheet-Role-Scavenger" name="attr_Role-Scavenger-Rebel"> <b>Rebel:</b> Mark
              when someone convinces you that your Family’s hoarding resources. Say one group whose suffering they could
              alleviate.</p>
            <p><input type="checkbox" class="sheet-Role-Scavenger" name="attr_Role-Scavenger-Outsider"> <b>Outsider:</b>
