            <p><input type="checkbox" class="sheet-Role-Untamed" name="attr_Role-Untamed-Rebel"> <b>Rebel:</b> Mark when
              you refuse to fight for your Family in a critical battle. Name something, anything, that'll survive the
              ordeal unharmed.</p>
